title: ITV’s new Cannonball show to bring barmy TV back to Saturday night where Total Wipeout left off
text:
TV Magazine BONKERS SATURDAY TV IS BACK ITV’s new Cannonball show to bring barmy TV back to Saturday night where Total Wipeout left off 
CHANNEL bosses are keen to fill the gap left when the BBC axed its 'Wipeout' show in 2013 by launching an even dafter one FROM DAN WOOTTON'S BIZARRE TV COLUMN 23rd February 2017, 10:08 pm
